\c 10
\p
\v 1 Panguva iyo Jehovha wakati kwandiri: Zvivezere mahwendefa maviri emabwe akafanana neekutanga, ugokwira kwandiri kugomo\x + Eki. 34.1,2.\x*; ugozviitira areka yematanda\x + Eki. 25.10.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino ndichanyora pamahwendefa mashoko aiva pamahwendefa ekutanga awakaputsa; ugoaisa muareka\x + Eki. 25.16,21.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino ndakaita areka \add ye\add*matanda emuakasia\x + Eki. 25.10. 37.1.\x*, ndokuveza mahwendefa maviri emabwe akafanana neekutanga, ndokukwira mugomo, nemahwendefa maviri ari muruoko rwangu\x + Eki. 34.4.\x*.
\v 4 Zvino wakanyora pamahwendefa zvichienderana nekunyora kwekutanga, mirairo gumi\x + Eki. 34.28.\x*, Jehovha yaakataura kwamuri mugomo kubva mukati memoto\x + Eki. 20.1.\x* pazuva reungano\x + 9.10.\x*; Jehovha ndokuapa kwandiri.
\v 5 Zvino ndakatendeuka ndokuburuka mugomo\x + Eki. 34.29.\x*, ndokuisa mahwendefa muareka yandaiva ndaita\x + Eki. 40.20.\x*. Zvino aripo ipapo, Jehovha sezvaakandiraira\x + 1 Madz. 8.9.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakabva paBheeroti-Bhene-Jakani\x + Num. 33.31.\x* kuenda kuMosera\x + Num. 33.30.\x*; ipapo Aroni wakafa, ndokuvigwapo\x + Num. 20.28. 33.38.\x*; Eriazari mwanakomana wake ndokushumira paupristi panzvimbo yake.
\v 7 Vachibvapo vakaenda kuGudhigodha; uye kubva paGudhigodha vakaenda kuJotibhati, nyika yehova dzemvura\x + Num. 33.32,33.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Panguva iyo Jehovha wakatsaura rudzi rwaRevhi\x + Num. 3.6. 8.14. 16.9.\x* kutakura areka yesungano yaJehovha\x + Num. 4.5,15.\x*, kumira pamberi paJehovha, kumushumira\x + 17.12. 18.5,7.\x*, nekuropafadza muzita rake, kusvika nhasi\x + Rev. 9.22.\x*.
\v 9 Naizvozvo Revhi haana mugove kana nhaka pamwe nehama dzake; Jehovha inhaka yake, Jehovha Mwari wako sezvaakamuvimbisa\x + Num. 18.20.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino ini ndakagara mugomo sepamazuva ekutanga, mazuva makumi mana neusiku makumi mana\x + 9.18.\x*; Jehovha ndokundinzwa panguva iyowo; Jehovha akasada kukuparadza\x + 9.19.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino Jehovha wakati kwandiri: Simuka enda parwendo pamberi pevanhu, kuti vapinde vagare nhaka yenyika, yandakapikira kumadzibaba avo kupa kwavari\x + Eki. 32.34. 33.1.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Zvino ikozvino, Israeri, chii Jehovha Mwari wako chaanoda kwauri\x + Mik. 6.8.\x*, kunze kwekutya Jehovha Mwari wako\x + 6.2.\x*, kufamba munzira dzake dzose\x + 5.33.\x*, nekumuda, nekushumira Jehovha Mwari wako nemoyo wako wose uye nemweya wako wose\x + 6.5.\x*,
\v 13 kuchengeta mirairo yaJehovha nezvimiso zvake zvandinokuraira nhasi kuti zvikunakire\x + 6.24.\x*?
\v 14 Tarira, matenga, nematenga ematenga, nyika, nezvose zviri mairi\x + Eki. 19.5. Map. 24.1. Gen.. 14.19.\x*, ndezvaJehovha Mwari wako\x + Map. 115.16. 1 Madz. 8.27. Map. 148.4.\x*.
\v 15 Koga Jehovha wakafarira madzibaba ako kuvada, ndokusarudza mbeu yavo shure kwavo, iyemwi, kubva pamarudzi ose, sanhasi\x + 4.37. Det. 7.7.\x*.
\v 16 Naizvozvo dzingisai chikanda chepamberi chemoyo wenyu\x + 30.6. Jer. 4.4. Eki. 6.12.\x*, musachiomesa mutsipa wenyu\x + 9.6.\x*.
\v 17 Nokuti Jehovha Mwari wenyu ndiMwari wevamwari\x + Josh. 22.22. Map. 136.2. Dhan. 2.47. 11.36.\x*, naIshe wemadzishe\x + Zvak. 17.14. 19.16.\x*, Mwari mukuru, ane masimba\x + 7.21.\x*, uye anotyisa\x + 7.21.\x*, asingasaruri zviso, kana kugamuchira fufuro\x + 2 Makor. 19.7. Job. 34.19. Mab. 10.34. VaRom. 2.11. VaGar. 2.6. VaEfe. 6.9. VaKoro. 3.25. 1 Pet. 1.17.\x*.
\v 18 Anotongera nherera nechirikadzi zvakarurama, uye anoda mutorwa pakumupa zvekudya nenguvo\x + Map. 68.5; 146.9; Eki.22.22.\x*.
\v 19 Naizvozvo muchada mutorwa, nokuti maiva vatorwa munyika yeEgipita\x + Rev. 19.33,34.\x*.
\v 20 Uchatya Jehovha Mwari wako; uchashumira iye\x + 6.2,13.\x*, uye uchanamatira paari\x + 11.22. 13.4. 30.20.\x*, uye uchapika nezita rake\x + 6.2,13.\x*.
\v 21 Ndiye rumbidzo yako, uye ndiMwari wako\x + Map.22.3. 109.1. Jer. 17.14.\x*, wakakuitira zvinhu izvi zvikuru uye zvinotyisa, meso ako zvaakaona\x + 2 Sam. 7.23; Map. 106.21,22.\x*.
\v 22 Madzibaba ako akaburukira kuEgipita ane vanhu makumi manomwe\x + Gen.. 46.27.\x*; zvino ikozvino Jehovha Mwari wako wakakuita uve senyeredzi dzematenga pakuwanda\x + Gen.. 15.5. Det.28.62. Neh. 9.23.\x*.
